snippet.title: Vigor – Nintendo Switch Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Become a Founder: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/vigor-switch/

Outlive the apocalypse, Vigor is a looter shooter in post-war Norway.

Shoot and loot in a tense encounters
Build your shelter and vital equipment
Challenge others in various game modes
Play on your own or fight together

🔪 Follow us 🔪
